UI-WELCOME_ERROR: 很抱歉，系统初始化存在异常，请仔细检查服务端配置
KIBANA-MUST_CONFIGURE_INDEX_PATTERN: 请配置至少一个有效的索引[注：检索数据与分析数据都必须基于索引]
KIBANA-CONTAINS_TIME_BASED_EVENTS: 索引包含基于时间序列的事件
KIBANA-INDEX_NAME_CREATED_BY_EVENT_TIMES: 请基于时间序列创建索引
KIBANA-ALERT_INDEX_PATTERN_DEPRECATED: 已废除基于时间间隔的索引模式!
KIBANA-WILD_CARD_PATTERN: using wildcard pattern names instead of time-interval based index patterns.
KIBANA-RECOMMEND_WILD_CARD_PATTERN_DETAI: Kibana is now smart enough to automatically determine which indices to search against within the current time range for wildcard index patterns. This means that wildcard index patterns now get the same performance optimizations when searching within a time range as time-interval patterns.
KIBANA-INDEX_NAME_OR_PATTERN: 请对名称或模式进行索引
KIBANA-WILDCARD_DYNAMIC_INDEX_PATTERNS: Patterns allow you to define dynamic index names using * as a wildcard. Example: logstash-*
KIBANA-STATIC_TEXT_IN_DYNAMIC_INDEX_PATT: Patterns allow you to define dynamic index names. Static text in an index name is denoted using brackets. Example: [logstash-]YYYY.MM.DD. Please note that weeks are setup to use ISO weeks which start on Monday.
KIBANA-WEEKLY_ISO_NOTICE: I noticed you are using weekly indices. Kibana requires ISO weeks be used in your index creation.
KIBANA-EXPAND_INDEX_PATTERN: 在检索过程中，请扩展搜索条件
KIBANA-WILDCARD_DEFAULT_EXPANDED_TO_CURR: With this option selected, searches against any time-based index pattern that contains a wildcard will automatically be expanded to query only the indices that contain data within the currently selected time range.
KIBANA-ACTUALLY_QUERY: will actually query Elasticsearch for the specific matching indices (e.g.
KIBANA-FALL_WITHIN_CURRENT_TIME_RANGE: ) that fall within the current time range.
KIBANA-EXPAND_INDEX_PATTERN_DEPRECATION: With recent changes to Elasticsearch, this option should no longer be necessary and will likely be removed in future versions of Kibana.
KIBANA-SAMPLE_ALERT: Attempted to match the following indices and aliases:
KIBANA-EXISTING_MATCH_PERCENT: Pattern matches {{indexExistingMatchPercent}} of existing indices and aliases
KIBANA-NON_MATCHING_INDICES_AND_ALIASES: 没有找到与索引模式相匹配的数据
KIBANA-NO_INDICES_MATCHING_PATTERN: 没有找到与模式匹配的索引
KIBANA-PATTERN_DOES_NOT_MATCH_EXIST_INDI: 索引模式与现存的索引都不匹配
KIBANA-INVALID_NON_UNIQUE_INDEX_NAME_CRE: Invalid pattern, interval does not create unique index names
KIBANA-FIELD_FILTER_EVENTS_GLOBAL_TIME: This field will be used to filter events with the global time filter
KIBANA-INTERVAL_INDEX_NAMES_ROTATE: The interval at which index names rotate.
KIBANA-NO_DEFAULT_INDEX_PATTERN: 请设置与数据相关的索引模式
KIBANA-INTERVAL_INDICES_POPULATED: 请在索引上选择时间间隔
KIBANA-INDICES_MATCH_PATTERN: 无法抓取映射文件，请确认是否存在这样的索引?
